    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Negative energy ripples out in a 60-foot-radius Sphere from a point you choose within range. Each creature in that area makes a Constitution saving throw, taking 12d6 Necrotic damage on a failed save or half as much damage on a successful one.</p><p><strong>Using a Higher-Level Spell Slot.</strong> The damage increases by 2d6 for each spell slot level above 6.</p><p>If you cast this spell using a level 9+ slot, the damage is 25d6 Necrotic damage.</p>",
